reviewtext: These headphones are great, but I could have saved $90 if I just kept using my, Panasonic RP-HTF600-S Stereo Headphones, instead of looking for "a better" pair of headphones to buy.  Also, these Sony headphones have the heavy coil wire which gets to be a little uncomfortable. The heavy coil wire makes it feel more tense as if the headphones are being pulled off your ears.
